---
import { Image } from '@astrojs/image/components'
import Layout from '@/components/Layout.astro'
import Banner from '@/components/Banner.astro'
---

<Layout title="Our Services - PURaFOG">
	<Banner title="What we do?" />
	<main>
		<div class="px-60">
			<section class="py-16 mt-8 centered">
				<div class="centered gap-8">
					<div
						class="pt-16 pb-12 px-6 w-[280px] h-[360px] rounded-xl bg-gradient-to-b from-green-500 to-green-800"
					>
						<div class="text-center text-white flex flex-col gap-2">
							<h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold capitalize">Mold remediation</h3>
							<p class="text-gray-50">
								Our atomized dry mist will eradicate molds, fungal matter, bacteria and viruses. We
								use an antifungal and antimicrobial treatments to eliminate mold colonies from
								forming.
							</p>
						</div>
					</div>

					<div
						class="pt-16 pb-12 px-6 w-[280px] h-[360px] rounded-xl bg-gradient-to-b from-green-500 to-green-800"
					>
						<div class="text-center text-white flex flex-col gap-2">
							<h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold capitalize">Virus sterilization</h3>
							<p class="text-gray-50">
								We use an organic hospital grade disinfectant to kill viruses that keeps your home
								or business sanitized. Our product is listed on the EPA List N for killing human
								coronavirus.
							</p>
						</div>
					</div>

					<div
						class="pt-16 pb-12 px-6 w-[280px] h-[360px] rounded-xl bg-gradient-to-b from-green-500 to-green-800"
					>
						<div class="text-center text-white flex flex-col gap-2">
							<h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold capitalize">Odor Elimination</h3>
							<p class="text-gray-50">
								Our product works through an oxidation chemical reaction that kills bacteria and
								fungus that causes odors. More specifically, it reacts on contact with the enzymes
								and proteins that make up simple cell organisms.
							</p>
						</div>
					</div>

					<div
						class="pt-16 pb-12 px-6 w-[280px] h-[360px] rounded-xl bg-gradient-to-b from-green-500 to-green-800"
					>
						<div class="text-center text-white flex flex-col gap-2">
							<h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold capitalize">Air Quality</h3>
							<p class="text-gray-50">
								We provide indoor air quality testing that we send to a 3rd party lab that
								specializes in analyzing samples to identify mold, bacteria, asbestos, and radon.
								These results help us make important decisions about the indoor environment
							</p>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</section>

			<section>
				<div class="grid grid-cols-3">
					<div class="col-span-2 px-8 flex flex-col gap-8">
						<h2 class="text-3xl mb-4 text-gray-600 font-semibold tracking-wide">
							Did you know that mold can be found almost everywhere? Mold grows naturally outside,
							but it can also grow almost anywhere indoors if moisture is present.
						</h2>

						<div>
							<div class="pb-6 border-b border-b-gray-400 flex gap-4">
								<div>
									<Image
										src="/img/green-checkmark.webp"
										alt="green checkmark"
										class="max-w-[34px]"
										width="128"
										height="128"
									/>
								</div>
								<span class="text-lg text-gray-600">
									We kill molds, allergens, toxins, viruses, pathogens.
								</span>
							</div>
						</div>

						<div>
							<div class="pb-6 border-b border-b-gray-400 centered gap-4">
								<div>
									<Image
										src="/img/green-checkmark.webp"
										alt="green checkmark"
										class="max-w-[34px]"
										width="128"
										height="128"
									/>
								</div>
								<span class="text-lg text-gray-600">
									We use an organic atomized dry mist that makes your air quality PURE again. This
									process requires no tearing down walls, just a few hours to get your house back to
									a healthy environment!
								</span>
							</div>
						</div>

						<div>
							<div class="pb-6 border-b border-b-gray-400 centered gap-4">
								<div>
									<Image
										src="/img/green-checkmark.webp"
										alt="green checkmark"
										class="max-w-[34px]"
										width="128"
										height="128"
									/>
								</div>
								<span class="text-lg text-gray-600">
									We use a Dry-mist disinfection system that disinfects the air and surfaces in
									enclosed areas by using chemical interaction of hydrogen peroxide. The different
									combination of hydrogen peroxide and positively charged ions offers the 99.99%
									kill rate. We complete the process by applying an antimicrobial surface protectant
									that provides continual protection for 90 days + Our formula has shown to
									eliminate a broad range of viruses and bacteria including superbugs like MRSA,
									H1N1, and Coronavirus variants â€“leaving behind a completely sterile environment.
								</span>
							</div>
						</div>

						<div>
							<div class="pb-6 centered gap-4">
								<div>
									<Image
										src="/img/green-checkmark.webp"
										alt="green checkmark"
										class="max-w-[34px]"
										width="128"
										height="128"
									/>
								</div>
								<span class="text-lg text-gray-600">
									We use an OMRI Listed, commercial sanitizer and disinfectant for use against human
									and plant pathogens, it is also kills the human coronavirus on surfaces.This
									organic product inhibits the growth of algae, bacteria, mold and mildew on hard,
									non-porous surfaces.
								</span>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>

					<div class="col-span-1 centered px-12 flex-col gap-12">
						<div
							class="text-gray-100 flex flex-col gap-4 px-8 py-12 rounded-lg shadow-xl bg-gradient-to-b from-green-500 to-green-800"
						>
							<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-center">How Can We Help?</h2>

							<div class="h-[1px] bg-gray-300"></div>

							<div class="flex flex-col gap-2">
								<div class="flex gap-3">
									<svg
										class="fill-gray-100 w-16 h-16"
										xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
										width="32"
										height="32"
										viewBox="0 0 512 512"
									>
										<path
											d="M164.9 24.6c-7.7-18.6-28-28.5-47.4-23.2l-88 24C12.1 30.2 0 46 0 64C0 311.4 200.6 512 448 512c18 0 33.8-12.1 38.6-29.5l24-88c5.3-19.4-4.6-39.7-23.2-47.4l-96-40c-16.3-6.8-35.2-2.1-46.3 11.6L304.7 368C234.3 334.7 177.3 277.7 144 207.3L193.3 167c13.7-11.2 18.4-30 11.6-46.3l-40-96z"
										></path>
									</svg>
									<span class="font-medium">
										<a href="tel:833-364-6653">833-364-6653 aka 833-FOG-MOLD (Call or text)</a>
									</span>
								</div>

								<div class="flex items-center gap-4">
									<svg
										class="fill-gray-100"
										xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
										width="32"
										height="32"
										viewBox="0 0 512 512"
									>
										<path
											d="M48 64C21.5 64 0 85.5 0 112c0 15.1 7.1 29.3 19.2 38.4L236.8 313.6c11.4 8.5 27 8.5 38.4 0L492.8 150.4c12.1-9.1 19.2-23.3 19.2-38.4c0-26.5-21.5-48-48-48H48zM0 176V384c0 35.3 28.7 64 64 64H448c35.3 0 64-28.7 64-64V176L294.4 339.2c-22.8 17.1-54 17.1-76.8 0L0 176z"
										></path>
									</svg>
									<a href="mailto:lisa@purafog.com" class="font-medium">Lisa@purafog.com</a>
								</div>
							</div>
						</div>

						<div>
							<Image
								src="/img/omri.png"
								width="320"
								height="128"
								alt="OMRI logo"
								style={{
									filter:
										'brightness(100%) contrast(100%) saturate(100%) blur(0px) hue-rotate(20deg)',
								}}
							/>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</section>

			<section class="py-16 mt-32 grid grid-cols-2 gap-8 border-t border-gray-300">
				<div class="col-span-1 centered gap-8">
					<div>
						<Image src="/img/nsf.png" width="160" height="160" alt="NSF Sustainability Certified" />
					</div>
					<div>
						<Image
							src="/img/epa.png"
							width="160"
							height="160"
							alt="EPA Environmental Protection Agency"
						/>
					</div>
					<div>
						<Image src="/img/made-in-usa.jpg" width="160" height="160" alt="Made in the USA" />
					</div>
				</div>

				<div class="col-span-1 flex flex-col gap-8 px-4">
					<div class="pb-6 border-b border-b-gray-400 centered gap-4">
						<div>
							<Image
								src="/img/green-checkmark.webp"
								alt="green checkmark"
								class="max-w-[34px]"
								width="128"
								height="128"
							/>
						</div>
						<span class="text-lg text-gray-600">
							Anti-microbial technology that provides persistent and continuous protection of a
							surface for up to 90 days that inhibits the growth of odor causing, and stain causing
							bacteria, mold, mildew, fungi, viruses and algae.
						</span>
					</div>

					<div class="pb-6 border-b border-b-gray-400 centered gap-4">
						<div>
							<Image
								src="/img/green-checkmark.webp"
								alt="green checkmark"
								class="max-w-[34px]"
								width="128"
								height="128"
							/>
						</div>
						<span class="text-lg text-gray-600">
							Air Quality Testing can be taken. The cartridges are sent to a 3rd party lab, these
							results show the type and counts in your air.
						</span>
					</div>
				</div>
			</section>
		</div>
	</main>
</Layout>
